{"tid":1400683,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[2014] 黎棟國：旺角地窄人多不宜催淚煙","createTime":"2019-08-03T13:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T17:40:12.000Z","uid":9800,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b6fda99ad4e3a0731aac60bccc2697148f38addf","tid":1400683,"uid":9800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:35:39.000Z","msg":"2014年10月4日星期六<br />\n<br />\n保安局長黎棟國表示，昨天旺角衝突現場環境相當狹窄，聚集人數很多，若放催淚煙驅散人群，會有危險。<br />\n<br />\n黎棟國召開記者會，被問到為何昨天只用人鏈而不用催淚彈控制情況，他回應說，現場地理環境相當狹窄，聚集人數很多，佔中和反佔中的群眾站在一起，中間是警員，若放催淚煙，情況會有危險，並不適宜。<br />\n<br />\n他又強調，特區政府全力支持警方以專業態度處理這些極難、人群極多的場面。"},{"pid":"6457271cc9d871b31a9be1149bca4de88ad6e882","tid":1400683,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:35:55.000Z","msg":"佢哋而家唔會理你咁多"},{"pid":"4fa210688b41f6aa1160c13e191be981989e0534","tid":1400683,"uid":9800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:36:12.000Z","msg":"???"},{"pid":"98826775b50261bb71c82643edd90b34909885c5","tid":1400683,"uid":9800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:37:37.000Z","msg":"記者朋友會唔會問下"},{"pid":"9e46456e3bca38394355278f47ce145701567bbf","tid":1400683,"uid":9800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:25:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9782110a3864e4efbc9b8fe72e9b0ae40e6e5289","tid":1400683,"uid":9800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:40:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}